
                ***** TREX WARRIOR - MINI DOCS *******

STEERING:      YOUR VEHICLE IS CONTROLLED BY YOUR MOUSE AND SOME KEYS OF 
               YOUR KEYBOARD.
               MOVE YOUR MOUSE TO THE LEFT OR RIGHT, TO TURN YOUR CRAFT.
               PRESS THE RIGHT MOUSEBUTTON AND MOVE THE MOUSE FORWARD TO 
               ACCELERATE OR BACKWARDS TO BRAKE.
               TO FIRE YOUR CANNON, PRESS THE LEFT BUTTON.

KEYS:         M -- SEIZES A TARGET IN FRONT OF YOUR CRAFT FOR FIGHTING IT 
                   WITH ROCKETS.
                   PLEASE NOTICE THAT THE TARGET INDICATOR FOR ROCKETS 
                   BACK TO THE NORMAL TARGET INDICATOR FOR CANNONS IF THE 
                   TARGET GETS OUT OF THE MIDDLE OF THE SCREEN.
                   PRESS THE LEFT MOUSEBUTTON TO START A ROCKET WHEN THE 
                   TARGET INDICATOR FOR ROCKETS IS ACTIVE.

              P -- STANDS FOR PAUSE.

              S -- TURNS ON A SOUNDFILTER THAT ABSORBS YOUR SHOOTING NOISES.

              HLP- RELEASES A SHOCKWAVE BOMB THAT DESTROYS
                   ALL OPPONENTS ON THE PLAYFIELD.

              SPC- THAT`S THE EMERGENCY BRAKE TO STOP YOUR
                   CRAFT IN THE SHORTEST DISTANCE WHETHER
                   YOU ARE MOVING FORWARD OR BACKWARDS.

TYPED IN BY CENOBYTES/CRYSTAL
